         <t:abstract>
            <t:p>This literary work of the Ethiopian <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS12520TaklaH">Catholic priest Takla Hāymānot</t:persName> describes the activity of Catholic missions in Ethiopia in <t:date>the middle of the 19th century</t:date>,
              and in  particular that of <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3451DeJacob">Giustino De Jacobis</t:persName>.</t:p>
         </t:abstract>
