                  <t:div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="1" xml:id="PartOne">
                     <t:label>Part 1</t:label>
                     <t:ab>እኔ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ በጽድቅ፡ ጸራኁህ፡ እጅኽንም፡ ያዝሁኽ፡ 
                        ጠበቅሁኽም፡ ለሕዝብም፡ ኪዳን፡ አደረግሁኽ፡ ለአሕዛብም፡ ብርሃን።</t:ab>                     
                  </t:div>
             
             <t:div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="2" xml:id="PartTwo">
                <t:label>Part 2</t:label>
                     <t:ab>ሙሴ፡ ሌዤአን፡ ሞንሰኘር፡ ደዢቆብ፡ የሚነቅፉበት፡</t:ab>                     
                  </t:div>
             
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="3" xml:id="PartThree">
               <t:label>Part 3</t:label>
                     <t:ab>በ፭ኛው፡ አኃዝ፡ እንዳየነ፡ ሙሴ፡ ሌዢአን፡ ሞንሰኘር፡ ደዢቆብ፡ ወደ፡ ምስር፡ መመለሳቸው፡ ነቅፈዋል።</t:ab>    
                  </t:div>
            
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="4" xml:id="PartFour">
               <t:label>Part 4</t:label>
                <t:ab>ሞንሰኘር፡ ደዢቆብ፡ ት፡ ፲፭ዓመት፡ ያህል፡ በትግሬ፡ ከኖሩ፡ በኋላ፡</t:ab>    
                  </t:div>
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="5" xml:id="PartFive">
               <t:label>Part 5</t:label>
                <t:ab>ታሪከ፡ ነገሥት፡ እንዳለ፡</t:ab>    
                  </t:div>
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="6" xml:id="PartSix">
               <t:label>Part 6</t:label>
                     <t:ab>ከዚህ፡ በፊት፡ እንዳልኍ፡ ራስ፡ ኃይሉና፡ ታላቁ፡ ራስ፡ ዓሊ፡</t:ab>
                  </t:div>
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="colophon" n="7" xml:id="Colophon">
               <t:label>Colophon</t:label>
               <t:ab>አነ፡ ካህን፡ <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS12520TaklaH">ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡</t:persName> ወልዱ፡ ለካህን፡ ተክለ፡ እግዚእ፡</t:ab>
            </t:div>
          </t:div>       
      </t:body>
     
